            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-zinc-300 rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center">
           <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-zinc-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 15.546c-.523 0-1.046.151-1.5.454a2.704 2.704 0 01-3 0 2.704 2.704 0 00-3 0 2.704 2.704 0 01-3 0 2.704 2.704 0 00-3 0 2.704 2.704 0 01-3 0 2.701 2.701 0 00-1.5-.454M9 6v2m3-2v2m3-2v2M9 3h.01M12 3h.01M15 3h.01M21 21v-7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v7h18zm-3-9v-2a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v2h12z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
         <h3 class="text-2xl uppercase font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-2">Reception</h3>
          <p class="text-xl text-zinc-700 mb-2">Same location</p>
          <p class="text-xl text-zinc-700 mb-2">Immediately following ceremony</p>
          <p class="text-xl text-zinc-700 ">Dinner & Dancing</p>
        </div>


      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story Section -->
  <section class="pb-8" id="about">
    <div class="euc-b"></div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 ">
      <h2 class="text-3xl text-center text-green font-600 uppercase mb-10">Our Story</h2>
      
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
            <div>
              <Image 
                src={import("../../assets/P1250505.jpg")} 
                alt="Couple Photo" 
                class="rounded-lg w-full h-auto"
              />

            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl mb-4 uppercase">How We Met</h3>
              <p>
                Jayden and Makenzie's story started back in their school days, though they were more like ships passing in the hallway—familiar faces, but not quite friends. Years later fate gave them a nudge through Jayden's cousin. They started hanging out, and what began as casual get-togethers quickly turned into something real. Their connection just clicked, and the rest is history.
              </p>

            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">

              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl mb-4 uppercase">The Proposal</h3>
                <p class=" mb-6">
                  On a trip to North Carolina, Jayden and Makenzie visited the stunning Biltmore Estate. While wandering through the gardens, they came across a quirky tree they dubbed the "asparagus tree". It was there, under that funny tree, that Jayden got down on one knee and proposed. It was a simple, heartfelt moment—perfectly them.
                </p>

               <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 items-center">
                 <Image 
                  src={import("../../assets/proposal-1.png")} 
                  alt="Couple Photo" 
                  class="rounded-lg h-full w-full"
                />
                 <Image 
                  src={import("../../assets/proposal-2.png")} 
                  alt="Couple Photo" 
                  class="rounded-lg h-full w-full"
                />
                
               </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <Image 
                  src={import("../../assets/proposal-4.jpg")} 
                  alt="Couple Photo" 
                  class="rounded-lg w-full h-auto"
                />

              </div>
          </div>

    </div>

  </section>

  <!-- Quote Section -->
  <section>
    <div class="bg-zinc-800 border-zinc-800 border-b border-t border-solid pt-5 pb-5">
       <p class="italic text-xl text-center"> "I will forever be thankful to God for gifting you to me. You are not just my partner; you are my best friend. I know I can always count on you. I love you so much." 
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>


